::Primal Prime::

    "What is it that you were carring? It seemed so familiar to me, yet so 
different." Primal Said. Just then he fainted. He was having another vision.
    This time he was fighting someone, but he didn't reconize him. He had a 
wound in his side that went through. Then he started to talk.
    "I thought you were made of strener stuff," He said to the figure on the 
ground. Suddenly Hot Rod, in a different body ran and grabbed the figure 
lying on the ground. Primal was shot and fell. His vision zoomed to another 
place entirely. The place was filled with Sparks. He was in the Matrix, again.
    He saw the Spark of Optimus Prime float to the Matrix to find peace, for 
it had been fighting for sometime now. He saw Cybertron, it was beautiful, 
and peaceful, no hate, no fighting. Then he saw that all change. The 
Cybertron he came from was very different then this one. He went into the 
past and saw something he had seen before. The Dark God Unicron came forth, 
with a Drake flying in front of it. Unicron started to change Cybertron to 
fit his vision of it.
    He slowly awoke from the vision. He saw Hot Rod and Striker. "How long 
have I been out?"
